			terms of clause 62 of the Standard General Conditions of the
			<lb />
			Contract, which contingency has been specifically kept out of the
			<lb />
			purview of the arbitration as per clause 63 of the General
			<lb />
			Conditions of the Contract.
			<lb />
			10. Mr. Gautam, learned counsel for the applicant submitted that
			<lb />
			as a consequence of pre-mature termination of the contract, the
