			<lb />
			notice under clause 62 was also issued by the Railways on
			<lb />
			17.07.2017. It will not be out of context to reproduce the notice
			<lb />
			dated 31.01.2018, which preceded the determination/termination
			<lb />
			of the subject contract.
			<lb />
		</body>
